scene.message:
SEBEC Employee: I always knew{nl}
this company had a dark side,{nl}
but...{waitkey}To think they were even making{nl}
biological weapons.{waitkey}{ret}

SEBEC Employee: The other day{nl}
in the office, I saw the ghost{nl}
of a girl in black clothes...{waitkey}{clearbox}It's got to be the curse of{nl}
the haunted house. Yes!{nl}
That must be it!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The haunted house, huh.{nl}
When I was little, I often{nl}
went there to play alone.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That Kandori!{waitkey}Turning the whole company{nl}
into his personal plaything{nl}
— what is he planning?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Such a pretty building,{nl}
but what they do inside is{nl}
the worst.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ghosts or biological{nl}
weapons, with me around{nl}
they're done for in a flash.{waitkey}{ret}
